      <title>世界银行援助将埃及的全球救助金额推至超过 500 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/world-bank-to-provide-egypt-with-over-6-billion-in-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行周一表示，将向埃及提供超过 60 亿美元的资金，使过去几周全球对这个北非国家陷入困境的经济的救助金额增加到超过 500 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/world-bank-to-provide-egypt-with-over-6-billion-in-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
